# Hackathon 2026

## How to run the project

1. Clone the repository:

   ```bash
    git clone https://github.com/HDDyer/Hackathon-2026
    cd Hackathon-2026
    ```
2. Ensure that you have Anaconda installed on your system. If not, you can download it from [here](https://www.anaconda.com/products/distribution) (you do not need a account to download Anaconda, find the small link "Skip Registration" on the download page).

3. Set up the backend environment:
    ```bash
     cd backend
     conda env create -f environment.yml
     conda activate backend
     python app.py
     ```